* She was hoping that he would know something about this, after all...it was 
his memories of the Matrix she had seen...somehow.
Iron Raptor just sighs, leaning back and then looking down at her hands.
Strange, she could almost pass for an organic...only her insides here all 
machine.
But then she suddenly heard a voice in her mind, much like Prowls.
Snapping her head to look up to him after the voice died away, though she 
had understood what he had said.
Though, it hurt her head a bit too.*

" What was that?"

* She spoke out loud.*
